<title>CANADA: RESEARCH ALERT - Cognos upgrade.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Cognos upgrade.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- UBS Securities said it upgraded Cognos Inc to strong buy from hold.</p>
<p>-- In a report, UBS said &quot;we are more comfortable today with the company's future product direction, which seemed to be at an interesting crossroads six months ago.&quot;</p>
<p>-- Raised estimate for fiscal year ending February 1998 to $1.10 from $1.04.</p>
<p>-- The stock rose 1-3/16 to 22-15/16.</p>
</text>
